data.description: Welcome home to this charming on story, conveniently located, within a short drive to downtown Sealy and local parks.   This home features a private pool, large fenced backyard, full length and a covered back porch.   The garage has an interior build out, which could serve as office space or an extra bunk area.    Kitchen and bath areas feature granite counters.   Utility room with built-in shelving is located inside the home.   No carpeting.  Primary bedroom has private access to the backyard and pool.   Lovely open concept.  All rooms measurements are approximate should be independently verified.  2 car covered carport.
